data.title: Imran Khan’s ex-wife Jemima Goldsmith spotted on date with Gary Lineker: Photos
data.meta_description: Imran Khan’s ex-wife, Jemima Goldsmith, was sighted enjoying a dinner date with former footballer, Gary Lineker.Photographed recently by Click News and Media, the two were located at a restaurant in Notting Hill, laughing and joking with...
data.text:
Imran Khan’s ex-wife, Jemima Goldsmith, was sighted enjoying a dinner date with former footballer, Gary Lineker.

Photographed recently by Click News and Media, the two were located at a restaurant in Notting Hill, laughing and joking with each other.

Both had planned an evening of entertainment in west London, but activities other than their time at the eatery are unknown.

As Gary Lineker stepped out with boxes of leftovers, Jemima Goldsmith quickly joined him for heading toward a car waiting together.

According to Daily Mail, she “giggled and kept her head down” while walking very closely to her alleged date.

The supposed pair spent a few minutes talking outside, where another unidentified female friend was also present.

All three of them had killed several hours by a window table at the bistro, sipping on wine as they relished some items from the menu.

Previously, Jemima Goldsmith had tied the knot with Pakistan’s former Prime Minister, Imran Khan, who she divorced in 2004.

After that, the socialite was romantically linked to high-profile celebrities Russell Brand and Hugh Grant.

Gary Lineker, on the other hand, married Michelle Cockayne in 1986, subsequently divorcing 20 years later.

He then got married to model Danielle Bux in 2009, but they also parted ways in 2016.
